'''蔗鼠'''是[[单型|单型科]]'''蔗鼠科'''（Thryonomyidae）下的2种较大型[[啮齿目|啮齿类动物]]的统称，分布于[[撒哈拉|撒哈拉]]以南的[[非洲|非洲]]。身材肥短，尾较短，耳小，毛粗硬，褐色带有小斑点。体长35-60厘米。其肉可食。一般栖息于临水处。善于游泳，被追赶时窜入水里。以根、禾草及植物其它部分为食。对甘蔗造成很大的损害。每窝产2-4仔，幼仔生下就有毛，睁眼。當地人有捕捉蔗鼠[[鼠肉#非洲|為食]]<ref name="bbc">{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/future/article/20151207-the-countries-where-rats-are-on-the-menu |first=Karl |last=Gruber |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] |title=While rats are met with revulsion in most parts of the world, some communities put rodents pride of place on the dinner menu |date=2015-12-07 |access-date=2021-08-14 |language=en |archive-date=2021-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211210033459/https://www.bbc.com/future/article/20151207-the-countries-where-rats-are-on-the-menu |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

